<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A teenager has been charged with attempted murder and firearms offences following a shooting in Suffolk where a 15-year-old boy was left in a critical condition. </p>

<p>Police raced to the scene shortly after 8.40am yesterday following reports that a teenage boy had been shot while walking to school in Kesgrave. </p>

